snippet.title: "Jim's Nightmare: Chapter 1" Official Pre-release Trailer
snippet.description:
Get an look into Jim's Nightmare with our pre-release trailer! Dive into the chilling world of this Detective Point & Click psychological horror game before its launch in just one month!
Wishlist and stay tuned🙌
